Scanner:
  filter errors by importance

Scenes:
  some actors may have additional contact area attached to his natural contact area. for example, human can hold a blade in the arm.

Scenes Papyrus API:
  get attribute value for desired scene. attribute defined by name and path of names. ex: "Authors", "Imported.Unknown"
  get scene's custom attribute. a) as a primitive, b) as a struct. if struct's string field points to a complex object -> init the field with a json string
  get actor's attributes.